f54-beed-6302bce56589&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Hulu&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJjYTE5ZGVhMC1lN2FkLTRmNTQtYmVlZC02MzAyYmNlNTY1ODkiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaHVsdS5jb20vYm9ubmFyb28iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQ3ZGIzNGUyLTFmZTktNDViYy1iZjk1LWNlZGVmNzVlNzFlZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbF3nmBCZzk64aNZ_epMpnajx-q8YEejr8XXYVrJ3KUm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hulu.com%2Fbonnaroo" class="rapid-with-clickid">查看平台的网站</a>以获取最新的时间表。不幸的是，事后你将无法在 Hulu 上播放这些场景——你必须收听现场直播才能看到它们。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>您需要成为 Hulu 订阅者才能观看直播，但该服务为新用户和符合条件的回访用户提供 7 天试用期。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lollapalooza-2021-live-stream-hulu-140043962.html">自 2021 年</a><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-07-31-youtube-lollapalooza-2019-live-stream.html">从 YouTube 手中</a>接管版权以来，Hulu 一直是 Bonnaroo 的流媒体之家。今年晚些时候，您还可以在该平台上观看 Lollapalooza 和 Austin City Limits 音乐节。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/hulu-is-streaming-bonnaroo-this-weekend-for-the-third-year-in-a-row-190034636.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hulu-is-streaming-bonnaroo-this-weekend-for-the-third-year-in-a-row-190034636.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d7db34e2-1fe9-45bc-bf95-cedef75e71ef</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 16 Jun 2023 19:00:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686940716</ingested><modified> 2023-06-16T18:38:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-